{{Infobox dungeon |name = Parfum Palace |image = [[File:Parfum Palace.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Parfum Palace. |tokens = 445,000 |location = West of Route 6. }} '''Parfum Palace''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile. Wild Encounters have 6,303,405 HP.
